I just want to say the best thing about you that you are one of the kindest people I've met at IITK jo critique bhi kare to aisa lagega ki taareef kaar raha ho lol. Aisa hi rehna bro hamesha plus keep doing whatever you do even if people say it's cringe because those things are what make you and define you. Even if we know that change is a constant in our lives, would tell you to not change these awesome things about you. 

Always be happy bro and remember that the car is on fire and there's no driver at the wheel :)

author: Yash  Maheshwari

text:
Mittal bhau!

Second year me mulakaat hui thi pehli baar shayad apni SnT presentation ke chalte, tum aur Ayush AUV ki presentation de rahe the aur hum Astro ki. Usse pehle koi mulakat bhul gaya ho to maaf karna bhai but tumse jab bhi baat ki hai hamesha achha laga hai. Tum aise baat karte ho ki kisi ko bhi hasa do, kaafi badhiya bande ho. E Cell bhi badi shaandaar tareeke se sambhala bhai tumne, dekhke badhiya laga tha tumhe aur Gupta ko as OC. Uske alawa zyada kaam to nahi kiya apan ne sath me but koi baat nahi uski jagah bulla badhiya kaata hua hai. 
SnT wale presentation se lekar apni Goa trip tak and BB par bhi, jab bhi tum kisi conversation me aate ho, hamesha mood light ho jata hai, hamesha aise hi mast bande rehna bhai. Abhi Goa trip pe to mile hi the apan sab, wapas milke baat karte hai kabhi, aur maze karenge. BB pe aur messenger pe to baate hoti hi rahengi but still Best of luck bhai aage ke liye! :)
author: Yash  Maheshwari

text:

Fir 2nd 3rd year me wing alag ho gayi thi to utna time nahi beeta paaye sath me but jab bhi milte the sahi baat hoti thi, fir 2nd year summer me bhi SPO team ke sath kaafi maze kiye the lol. Randomly hall 2 chale jana and ek baar raat me cafe bhi chale gaye the aise hi. SPO kaafi achhe se sambhal liya bhai tune aise online tenure me and kaafi help bhi kari ek dusre ki usme, thanks for that bhai!
Ek last baar milna reh gaya bhai campus me, uski kami puri karne ke liye milte hai wapas kisi din! Best of luck bro Japan ke liye tujhe, stay happy! :)

text:
Tarish bhai!

First year me mila tha tujhse mess me pehli baar, uske baad se tera fan ho gaya tha lol. Your knowledge on almost every topic out there and ekdum lit timing wale references were the best. Kaafi time bitaya sath me, 2nd year to ig aadha tere room pe hi beeta tha not to forget all those times in the Astro club lol. Last me FLP bhi kar liya apan ne sath me which we wanted to do. Thanks for all those anime recs too btw, abhi bhi follow kar raha sabko. Itni baate ki hai apan ne ki can't sum up all of that in one memoir and pretty sure abhi idhar aur likha to feels trip pe chala jaunga mai. So sorry agar kuch likha nahi idhar lol. Other than that bro baat kar liya kar kabhi discord ya whatsapp pe, have been trying to contact you ig ye padhke shayad contact kare. 

I hope we always stay connected in the future and let's meet up surely kabhi!
